**###BEFORE_INPUT###****###BEFORE_INPUT###****###AFTER_INPUT###****###AFTER_INPUT###****###WHEN_FIELD_CHANGE###****###WHEN_FIELD_CHANGE###****###BUTTON_CLICKED###**<BUTTONS ExecScriptOnChange="0"> <BUTTON Name="Edit Email Adresses" Script="NLSApp.SaveScreen() EmailUpdate()
Sub EmailUpdate() cifref = NLSapp.GetField("CIF_REFNO") cifnumber = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_NUMBER") cifport = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_PORTFOLIO") If cifport = "FREEDOM PLUS BORROWER" Then mailonly = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_DETAIL_UDF7") Else mailonly = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_DETAIL_UDF3") End If curremail1 = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_EMAIL1") curremail2 = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_EMAIL2")
cifacctrefsql = "SELECT distinct convert(varchar,l.acctrefno) from loanacct l, cif c where l.cifno = c.cifno and c.cifno = " & cifref
cifacctref = NLSApp.SQLSelectStatement(cifacctrefsql)
currentconfigmsgp1 = "Current Email Address for " & cifnumber
currentconfigmsg = currentconfigmsgp1 & chr(10) & chr(10) & curremail1 & chr(10) & _ chr(10) & chr(10) & "Edit? (Y/N)"
If NLSApp.YesNoMessageBox(currentconfigmsg) Then newemail = addnewemail (cifnumber,1) If Not newemail = "" Then NLSapp.AddModificationHistory 0, cifref, curremail1,newemail, "Primary Email" NLSApp.MessageBox("Added.") End If
NLSApp.RefreshScreen() Else msgbox("Canceling") End If End Sub
Function addnewemail(contactnum,emailno) retry = True
commprefidsql = "select Distinct convert(varchar,lcp.LoanCommunicationPreferencesID)" & chr(13) & _ "from cif c,loanacct l, LoanCommunicationPreferences lcp" & chr(13) & _ "where l.cifno = c.cifno and l.acctrefno = lcp.acctrefno and c.cifnumber = '" & contactnum & "'" 'NLSApp.MessageBox(commprefidsql) commprefid = NLSApp.SQLSelectStatement(commprefidsql) 'NLSApp.MessageBox(commprefidsql) Do eaddress = InputBox("Please enter a valid email address.","New Email" & emailno, "some.thing@somewhere.com") ' email format check exchnage = InStrRev(eaddress, "@") domain = InStrRev(eaddress, ".") If not eaddress = "" Then If (Not exchnage = 0 and Not domain = 0) And (exchnage < domain) Then
If emailno = 1 Then addressedits1 = "SELECT 0; UPDATE cif SET email = '" & eaddress & "' where cifnumber = '" & contactnum & "'" & chr(13)& _ "DELETE FROM LoanCommunicationAddress where LoanCommunicationPreferencesID = " & commprefid & chr(13) & _ "INSERT INTO LoanCommunicationAddress Values (" & commprefid & ", '" & eaddress & "', 0)" Else addressedits1 = "SELECT 0; UPDATE cif SET email2 = '" & eaddress & "' where cifnumber = '" & contactnum & "'" & chr(13) End If
NLSApp.SQLSelectStatement addressedits1 retry = False Else retry = NLSApp.YesNoMessageBox("Invalid Email format" & chr(10) & chr(10) &"Retry? (Y/N)")
If retry = false Then addnewemail = "" Exit Do End if End if Else MsgBox("Canceling") Exit Do End if addnewemail = eaddress Loop while retry = True End Function"/> <BUTTON Name="Delete Current Email Addresses" Script="NLSApp.SaveScreen() EmailDelete()
Sub EmailDelete() cifref = NLSapp.GetField("CIF_REFNO") cifnumber = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_NUMBER") cifport = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_PORTFOLIO") If cifport = "FREEDOM PLUS BORROWER" Then mailonly = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_DETAIL_UDF7") Else mailonly = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_DETAIL_UDF3") End If If mailonly = "UNCHECK" Then NLSApp.MessageBox("You cannot Delete an email address unless the borrower has opted for MAIL ONLY communication." & chr(10) & chr(10) & "Canceling.") Exit sub End if curremail1 = NLSApp.GetField("CIF_EMAIL1")
commprefidsql = "select Distinct convert(varchar,lcp.LoanCommunicationPreferencesID)" & chr(13) & _ "from cif c,loanacct l, LoanCommunicationPreferences lcp" & chr(13) & _ "where l.cifno = c.cifno and l.acctrefno = lcp.acctrefno and c.cifnumber = '" & cifnumber & "'"
commprefid = NLSApp.SQLSelectStatement(commprefidsql) currentconfigmsgp1 = "Current Email Address for " & cifnumber currentconfigmsg = currentconfigmsgp1 & chr(10) & chr(10) & curremail1 & chr(10) & _ chr(10) & chr(10) & "Delete? (Y/N)"
If NLSApp.YesNoMessageBox(currentconfigmsg) Then
addressdelete = "SELECT 0; UPDATE cif SET email = NULL, email2 = NULL where cifnumber = '" & cifnumber & "'" & chr(13) & _ "DELETE FROM LoanCommunicationAddress where LoanCommunicationPreferencesID = " & commprefid NLSApp.SQLSelectStatement addressdelete NLSapp.AddModificationHistory 0, cifref, curremail1, "", "Primary Email" NLSApp.MessageBox("Removed.") NLSApp.RefreshScreen() Else msgbox("Canceling") End If End Sub"/> </BUTTONS> **###BUTTON_CLICKED###****###ON_FIELD_REFRESH###****###ON_FIELD_REFRESH###****###ON_INITIALIZE###****###ON_INITIALIZE###**

'SUB scripts '----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Sub Emailsync() 'Automation to keep the cif.email1 field in sync with the LoanCommunicationAddress.Address field '------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ email1sql = "SELECT distinct top 1 cmh.new_value" & chr(13) & _ ",cmh.mod_datestamp" & chr(13) & _ "FROM cif cif, cif_modification_history cmh" & chr(13) & _ "WHERE cif.cifno = cmh.cifno" & chr(13) & _ "AND cmh.item_changed = 'Email1'" & chr(13) & _ "and datediff(mm,cmh.mod_datestamp,getdate()) < 60" & chr(13) & _ "AND cif.cifno = " & cifno & chr(13) & _ "order by cmh.mod_datestamp desc"
emailcommsql = "Select lca.address" & chr(13) & _ "from loanacct la,LoanCommunicationPreferences lcp, LoanCommunicationAddress lca" & chr(13) & _ "where la.acctrefno = lcp.acctrefno" & chr(13) & _ "and lcp.LoanCommunicationPreferencesID = lca.LoanCommunicationPreferencesID" & chr(13) & _ "and la.cifno = " & cifno
acctrefnosql = "Select convert(varchar(11),acctrefno) from loanacct where cifno = " & cifno
email1 = NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement(email1sql) emailcomm = NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement(emailcommsql) acctrefno = NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement(acctrefnosql)
'When email1 is NULL do nothing If email1 <> "" Then 'When email1 and comm-email already match do nothing If email1 <> emailcomm Then 'When comm-email1 is empty only add email1 to comm If emailcomm = "" Then Commxml = "<NLS>" & chr(13) & _ " <LOAN UpdateFlag=""1"" AcctRefno=""" & acctrefno & """>" & chr(13) & _ " <COMMUNICATION>" & chr(13) & _ " <EMAILADDRESSES>" & chr(13) & _ " <EMAILADDRESS Operation=""ADD"" Address=""" & email1 & """/>" & chr(13) & _ " </EMAILADDRESSES>" & chr(13) & _ " </COMMUNICATION>" & chr(13) & _ " </LOAN>" & chr(13) & _ "</NLS>" Else Commxml = "<NLS>" & chr(13) & _ " <LOAN UpdateFlag=""1"" AcctRefno=""" & acctrefno & """>" & chr(13) & _ " <COMMUNICATION>" & chr(13) & _ " <EMAILADDRESSES>" & chr(13) & _ " <EMAILADDRESS Operation=""DELETE"" Address=""" & emailcomm & """/>" & chr(13) & _ " </EMAILADDRESSES>" & chr(13) & _ " </COMMUNICATION>" & chr(13) & _ " </LOAN>" & chr(13) & _ " <LOAN UpdateFlag=""1"" AcctRefno=""" & acctrefno & """>" & chr(13) & _ " <COMMUNICATION>" & chr(13) & _ " <EMAILADDRESSES>" & chr(13) & _ " <EMAILADDRESS Operation=""ADD"" Address=""" & email1 & """/>" & chr(13) & _ " </EMAILADDRESSES>" & chr(13) & _ " </COMMUNICATION>" & chr(13) & _ " </LOAN>" & chr(13) & _ "</NLS>" End If ImportXML(Commxml) End if End if End Sub**###After Save###****###After Create###****###After Create###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###Local Functions###**'--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 'Port form function #1 'XML Import '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Function ImportXML(xml) NLSApp.ClearErrorString()
